        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Cloning a PDF page does not work as expected or documented.\r\nWhen trying to make a working example out of [http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.pdf.pages.html#zend.pdf.pages.cloning] it throws an exception\r\n{{Uncaught exception 'Zend_Pdf_Exception' with message 'Font has not been set'}}\r\nevent if the original page has a font set which should be cloned, too.\r\n{code:title=Example}\r\n$templatePageIndex = 'template';\r\n$pdf = new Zend_Pdf();\r\n$page = new Zend_Pdf_Page(Zend_Pdf_Page::SIZE_A4_LANDSCAPE);\r\n$page->setFont(Zend_Pdf_Font::fontWithName(Zend_Pdf_Font::FONT_HELVETICA), 11);\r\n$pdf->pages[$templatePageIndex] = $page;\r\n$template = $pdf->pages[$templatePageIndex];\r\n$page1 = new Zend_Pdf_Page($template);\r\n$page1->drawText('Some text...', 10, 10);\r\n{code}"
        },
